
PIDA Readme
===========

PIDA is an IDE.


Quick Installation Instructions
==============================

To install PIDA, run:

    python setup.py install

You may require super user access depending on where you want to install it.

Then you can run PIDA by executing the command

    pida

Run Without Installing
======================

If you wish to run pida without installation, run the developer.sh script in
the top-level directory.

More Information
================

For more information, requirements etc please read the manual in docs/.

Contact me directly if you have any problems.

Website: http://pida.vm.bytemark.co.uk/



